# SMA-437 Layer-1 per-netns IPv6 default-deny companion to netns-deny.rules.
# Applied inside each child netns alongside the IPv4 ruleset.
# Default-deny all IPv6 egress. No proxy/DNS allow rules here: the egress proxy
# and DNS resolver are reached over IPv4 in this harness — IPv6 traffic has no
# permitted path and is dropped entirely.
*filter
:OUTPUT DROP [0:0]
-A OUTPUT -o lo -j ACCEPT
-A OUTPUT -m state --state ESTABLISHED,RELATED -j ACCEPT
COMMIT
